<DocsLayout title="Team Management" section="Auxiliary Modules">
  <h2>Overview</h2>
  <p>
    Manage teams efficiently in Field Promax by using Work Groups and Team Leads.
    Give technicians the ability to view other technicians' work orders without
    making them full administrators.
  </p>
  <p>
    When managing a large team, having Team Leads helps reduce the load on office admins.
    Field Promax makes this seamless, allowing Team Leads to manage their team without
    requiring full administrative access.
  </p>

  <h2>How to Access</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Go to <strong>Settings</strong> → <strong>Manage Lists</strong> → <strong>Work Groups</strong> to create a Work Group</li>
    <li>Go to <strong>Settings</strong> → <strong>Manage Users</strong> to assign technicians</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Setting Up Teams</h2>

  <h3>Step 1: Create a Work Group</h3>
  <ol>
    <li>Go to <strong>Settings</strong> → <strong>Manage Lists</strong> → <strong>Work Groups</strong></li>
    <li>Create a new Work Group for your team</li>
  </ol>

  <h3>Step 2: Assign Technicians</h3>
  <img src="/images/auxiliary-modules/auxillarymodules_teammanagement_01.webp" alt="Assign Technicians" />
  <ol>
    <li>Go to <strong>Settings</strong> → <strong>Manage Users</strong></li>
    <li>Select each technician and assign them to the Work Group</li>
  </ol>

  <h3>Step 3: Designate Team Lead</h3>
  <img src="/images/auxiliary-modules/auxillarymodules_teammanagement_02.webp" alt="Assign Team Lead" />
  <ol>
    <li>Select the technician who will be Team Lead</li>
    <li>Assign the Work Group to them</li>
    <li>This allows them to view work orders from other technicians in their team</li>
  </ol>

  <h2>Team Lead Capabilities</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>View work orders for all team members</li>
    <li>Monitor team progress</li>
    <li>Help with coordination without full admin access</li>
    <li>Cannot modify system settings or other administrative functions</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Notifications & Permissions</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Only <strong>Administrators</strong> can assign and manage Work Groups</li>
    <li>Team Leads can view other technicians' work orders without administrative permissions</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Tips</h2>
  <div class="callout callout-tip">
    <p>
      <strong>Utilize Team Leads effectively</strong> — assign experienced technicians to help manage their peers.
    </p>
    <p>
      <strong>Create logical Work Groups</strong> based on geography, skill set, or service type.
    </p>
    <p>
      <strong>Review team assignments</strong> regularly as your workforce changes.
    </p>
  </div>
</DocsLayout>
